headline: RTX (RTX): Evaluating Valuation Following Major Defense Wins and Growing Backlog
summary: RTX has been making headlines with a series of major defense contracts, including a $1.7 billion radar deal and a $578.6 million Stinger missile order. Raytheon’s recent ESSM Block 2 missile milestone further showcases steady demand for the company’s core technologies. See our latest analysis for RTX.
